    <h3>Skip the gym for some time </h3>
    <p>Give activities like hot showers and exercise sessions a miss for the first 24 to 48 hours. After a laser  session due to heat your skin becomes more sensitive, and sweating could lead to irritation.</p>
    <h3>Say no to hair removal methods</h3> 
